    title: 'ScandyCandy Review 2026: The Swedish Candy Store That Sold Out in 9 Days',
    silo: 'where-to-buy',
    seoTitle: 'ScandyCandy Review 2026: Coral Gables Swedish Candy Store | SwedishCrave',
